snippet: A Syrian rebel commander has been shot dead in the Jordanian capital in the first such incident on the kingdom's territory since the start of the conflict in Syria in 2011, a police source said on Saturday....

headline.print_headline: Syrian Rebel Commander Assassinated in Jordan: Police
headline.main: Syrian Rebel Commander Assassinated in Jordan: Police

lead_paragraph: A Syrian rebel commander has been shot dead in the Jordanian capital in the first such incident on the kingdom's territory since the start of the conflict in Syria in 2011, a police source said on Saturday.
